<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Frank Ocean"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Blonde"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Nikes"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="426194881"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="QZ5C81600001"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="190055247"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="DEVILISALIE"/></metadata></head><body dur="04:52.802"><div begin="00:27.566" end="04:52.802"><p begin="00:27.566" end="00:32.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L0"><span begin="00:27.566" end="00:27.813">These</span> <span begin="00:27.813" end="00:27.932">bit</span><span begin="00:27.932" end="00:28.159">ches</span> <span begin="00:28.159" end="00:28.628">want</span> <span begin="00:28.628" end="00:29.236">Ni</span><span begin="00:29.236" end="00:32.200">kes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些泼妇想要买耐克</span></p><p begin="00:34.597" end="00:36.046" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:34.597" end="00:34.672">They</span> <span begin="00:34.672" end="00:34.918">loo</span><span begin="00:34.918" end="00:35.146">king</span> <span begin="00:35.146" end="00:35.248">for</span> <span begin="00:35.248" end="00:35.495">a</span> <span begin="00:35.495" end="00:36.046">check</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他们在寻找能为她们开支票的人（check双关支票和耐克logo）</span></p><p begin="00:37.709" end="00:41.027" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:37.709" end="00:37.959">Tell</span> <span begin="00:37.959" end="00:38.220">'em</span> <span begin="00:38.220" end="00:38.393">it</span> <span begin="00:38.393" end="00:38.832">ain't</span> <span begin="00:38.832" end="00:39.321">like</span><span begin="00:39.321" end="00:41.027">ly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">并告诉他们事实并非如此</span></p><p begin="00:41.629" end="00:47.322" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:41.629" end="00:41.835">Said</span> <span begin="00:41.835" end="00:42.064">she</span> <span begin="00:42.064" end="00:42.261">need</span> <span begin="00:42.261" end="00:42.522">a</span> <span begin="00:42.522" end="00:43.158">ring</span> <span begin="00:43.158" end="00:43.623">like</span> <span begin="00:43.623" end="00:44.131">Car</span><span begin="00:44.131" end="00:45.078">me</span><span begin="00:45.078" end="00:47.322">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">她想要一枚戒指，就像卡梅隆·安东尼（Carmelo Anthony，NBA名宿）手上的NBA总冠军戒指</span></p><p begin="00:48.525" end="00:54.541" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:48.525" end="00:48.650">You</span> <span begin="00:48.650" end="00:48.818">must</span> <span begin="00:48.818" end="00:49.033">be</span> <span begin="00:49.033" end="00:49.217">on</span> <span begin="00:49.217" end="00:49.490">that</span> <span begin="00:49.490" end="00:50.107">white</span> <span begin="00:50.107" end="00:50.508">like</span> <span begin="00:50.508" end="00:50.980">O</span><span begin="00:50.980" end="00:52.093">thel</span><span begin="00:52.093" end="00:54.541">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也会像奥赛罗（莎士比亚笔下的黑人角色）那样因为吸了白粉后而情绪高昂</span></p><p begin="00:55.579" end="00:59.334" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:55.579" end="00:55.782">All</span> <span begin="00:55.782" end="00:56.040">you</span> <span begin="00:56.040" end="00:56.262">want</span> <span begin="00:56.262" end="00:56.501">is</span> <span begin="00:56.501" end="00:57.028">Ni</span><span begin="00:57.028" end="00:59.334">kes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你只想要神话中的女神</span></p><p begin="00:59.559" end="01:00.923" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:59.559" end="00:59.756">But</span> <span begin="00:59.756" end="00:59.974">the</span> <span begin="00:59.974" end="01:00.532">real</span> <span begin="01:00.532" end="01:00.923">ones</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是这世界如此真实</span></p><p begin="01:02.781" end="01:05.931" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:02.781" end="01:03.097">Just</span> <span begin="01:03.097" end="01:03.721">like</span> <span begin="01:03.721" end="01:05.931">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像你那样</span></p><p begin="01:06.235" end="01:09.628" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:06.235" end="01:06.603">Just</span> <span begin="01:06.603" end="01:07.239">like</span> <span begin="01:07.239" end="01:09.628">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像我这样</span></p><p begin="01:10.264" end="01:15.770" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:10.264" end="01:10.386">I</span> <span begin="01:10.386" end="01:10.781">don't</span> <span begin="01:10.781" end="01:12.353">play,</span> <span begin="01:12.353" end="01:12.567">I</span> <span begin="01:12.567" end="01:13.162">don't</span> <span begin="01:13.162" end="01:13.614">make</span> <span begin="01:13.614" end="01:15.770">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我没有伪装 也没有刻意制造时间</span></p><p begin="01:16.668" end="01:22.909" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:16.668" end="01:16.832">But</span> <span begin="01:16.832" end="01:17.010">if</span> <span begin="01:17.010" end="01:17.308">you</span> <span begin="01:17.308" end="01:17.925">need</span> <span begin="01:17.925" end="01:18.338">dick</span> <span begin="01:18.338" end="01:18.806">I</span> <span begin="01:18.806" end="01:19.884">got</span> <span begin="01:19.884" end="01:20.286">you</span> <span begin="01:20.286" end="01:20.539">and</span> <span begin="01:20.539" end="01:20.796">I</span> <span begin="01:20.796" end="01:21.422">yam</span> <span begin="01:21.422" end="01:21.867">from</span> <span begin="01:21.867" end="01:22.269">the</span> <span begin="01:22.269" end="01:22.909">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是如果你需要誓言 我会向你承诺 我会不惜一切为你争取</span></p><p begin="01:23.365" end="01:26.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:23.365" end="01:23.611">Pour</span> <span begin="01:23.611" end="01:24.037">up</span> <span begin="01:24.037" end="01:24.283">for</span> <span begin="01:24.283" end="01:24.916">A</span><span begin="01:24.916" end="01:26.560">$AP</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">向A$AP Yams致以敬意</span></p><p begin="01:26.861" end="01:29.424" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:26.861" end="01:27.058">R.</span><span begin="01:27.058" end="01:27.286">I.</span><span begin="01:27.286" end="01:27.723">P.</span> <span begin="01:27.723" end="01:28.374">Pimp</span> <span begin="01:28.374" end="01:29.424">C</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为为嘻哈传奇Pimp C深感惋惜</span></p><p begin="01:30.326" end="01:36.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:30.326" end="01:30.564">R.</span><span begin="01:30.564" end="01:30.802">I.</span><span begin="01:30.802" end="01:31.251">P.</span> <span begin="01:31.251" end="01:31.824">Tray</span><span begin="01:31.824" end="01:33.081">von,</span> <span begin="01:33.228" end="01:33.408">that</span> <span begin="01:33.408" end="01:33.619">nig</span><span begin="01:33.619" end="01:33.873">ga</span> <span begin="01:33.873" end="01:34.072">look</span> <span begin="01:34.072" end="01:34.517">just</span> <span begin="01:34.517" end="01:35.150">like</span> <span begin="01:35.150" end="01:36.810">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为特雷文（2·26美国黑人男孩被杀案受害者），一个看起来像我一样的家伙深感惋惜</span></p><p begin="01:38.608" end="01:45.836" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:38.608" end="01:41.047">Woo,</span> <span begin="01:41.293" end="01:41.594">fu</span><span begin="01:41.594" end="01:42.164">ckin'</span> <span begin="01:42.164" end="01:42.387">buz</span><span begin="01:42.387" end="01:43.921">zin',</span> <span begin="01:43.921" end="01:45.836">woo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哇，真他妈烦人，哇</span></p><p begin="01:45.981" end="01:49.181" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:45.981" end="01:46.183">That</span> <span begin="01:46.183" end="01:46.451">my</span> <span begin="01:46.451" end="01:46.580">lit</span><span begin="01:46.580" end="01:46.858">tle</span> <span begin="01:46.858" end="01:47.037">cou</span><span begin="01:47.037" end="01:47.276">sin,</span> <span begin="01:47.511" end="01:47.717">he</span> <span begin="01:47.717" end="01:47.939">got</span> <span begin="01:47.939" end="01:48.165">a</span> <span begin="01:48.165" end="01:48.326">lit</span><span begin="01:48.326" end="01:48.590">tle</span> <span begin="01:48.590" end="01:49.181">trade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的小堂弟做起了一桩小生意</span></p><p begin="01:51.095" end="01:54.237" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:51.095" end="01:51.287">His</span> <span begin="01:51.287" end="01:51.692">girl</span> <span begin="01:51.692" end="01:51.860">keep</span> <span begin="01:51.860" end="01:52.082">the</span> <span begin="01:52.082" end="01:52.544">scales,</span> <span begin="01:52.752" end="01:52.915">a</span> <span begin="01:52.915" end="01:53.118">lit</span><span begin="01:53.118" end="01:53.429">tle</span> <span begin="01:53.429" end="01:53.847">mer</span><span begin="01:53.847" end="01:54.237">maid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他的女朋友没少受惩罚 就像小美人鱼一样</span></p><p begin="01:54.709" end="01:57.751" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:54.709" end="01:54.893">We</span> <span begin="01:54.893" end="01:55.131">out</span> <span begin="01:55.131" end="01:55.334">by</span> <span begin="01:55.334" end="01:55.556">the</span> <span begin="01:55.556" end="01:55.940">pool,</span> <span begin="01:56.221" end="01:56.389">some</span> <span begin="01:56.389" end="01:56.554">lit</span><span begin="01:56.554" end="01:56.850">tle</span> <span begin="01:56.850" end="01:57.284">mer</span><span begin="01:57.284" end="01:57.751">maids</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们在泳池边看见了几条美人鱼</span></p><p begin="01:58.177" end="01:59.482" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:58.177" end="01:58.360">Me</span> <span begin="01:58.360" end="01:58.585">and</span> <span begin="01:58.585" end="01:59.028">them</span> <span begin="01:59.028" end="01:59.482">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我和他们都喷了发胶</span></p><p begin="01:59.700" end="02:01.366" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:59.700" end="01:59.848">Like</span> <span begin="01:59.848" end="02:00.309">twigs</span> <span begin="02:00.309" end="02:00.495">with</span> <span begin="02:00.495" end="02:00.719">them</span> <span begin="02:00.719" end="02:01.366">bangs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">好像刘海上长出了细枝</span></p><p begin="02:02.741" end="02:04.841" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:02.741" end="02:02.908">Now</span> <span begin="02:02.908" end="02:03.104">that's</span> <span begin="02:03.104" end="02:03.361">a</span> <span begin="02:03.361" end="02:03.813">real</span> <span begin="02:03.813" end="02:04.259">mer</span><span begin="02:04.259" end="02:04.841">maid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">既然这是条真正的美人鱼</span></p><p begin="02:05.181" end="02:07.732" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:05.181" end="02:05.340">You</span> <span begin="02:05.340" end="02:05.489">been</span> <span begin="02:05.489" end="02:05.621">hol</span><span begin="02:05.621" end="02:05.794">ding</span> <span begin="02:05.794" end="02:06.207">your</span> <span begin="02:06.207" end="02:07.732">breath</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你一直在屏息很久</span></p><p begin="02:08.386" end="02:11.742" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:08.386" end="02:08.710">Weigh</span><span begin="02:08.710" end="02:10.009">ted</span> <span begin="02:10.009" end="02:11.742">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不断下沉</span></p><p begin="02:12.500" end="02:17.064" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:12.500" end="02:12.934">Punk</span> <span begin="02:12.934" end="02:13.464">ma</span><span begin="02:13.464" end="02:14.214">dre</span> <span begin="02:14.214" end="02:14.625">punk</span> <span begin="02:14.625" end="02:15.254">pa</span><span begin="02:15.254" end="02:17.064">pá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">虚伪的爸爸妈妈</span></p><p begin="02:19.481" end="02:21.519" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:19.481" end="02:19.645">He</span> <span begin="02:19.645" end="02:19.946">don't</span> <span begin="02:19.946" end="02:20.589">care</span> <span begin="02:20.589" end="02:20.987">for</span> <span begin="02:20.987" end="02:21.519">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他不喜欢我</span></p><p begin="02:22.936" end="02:24.895" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:22.936" end="02:23.127">But</span> <span begin="02:23.127" end="02:23.375">he</span> <span begin="02:23.375" end="02:24.021">cares</span> <span begin="02:24.021" end="02:24.465">for</span> <span begin="02:24.465" end="02:24.895">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是他又关心我</span></p><p begin="02:26.250" end="02:30.559" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:26.250" end="02:26.406">And</span> <span begin="02:26.406" end="02:26.747">that's</span> <span begin="02:26.747" end="02:29.972">good</span> <span begin="02:29.972" end="02:30.156">e</span><span begin="02:30.156" end="02:30.559">nough</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那已经很好了</span></p><p begin="02:33.310" end="02:35.902" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:33.310" end="02:33.455">We</span> <span begin="02:33.455" end="02:33.848">don't</span> <span begin="02:33.848" end="02:34.477">talk</span> <span begin="02:34.477" end="02:35.106">much</span> <span begin="02:35.106" end="02:35.325">or</span> <span begin="02:35.325" end="02:35.543">no</span><span begin="02:35.543" end="02:35.902">thin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们谈的话不多也不少</span></p><p begin="02:36.581" end="02:39.596" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:36.581" end="02:36.816">But</span> <span begin="02:36.816" end="02:36.987">when</span> <span begin="02:36.987" end="02:37.248">we</span> <span begin="02:37.248" end="02:37.682">tal</span><span begin="02:37.682" end="02:37.920">kin'</span> <span begin="02:37.920" end="02:38.574">'bout</span> <span begin="02:38.574" end="02:38.791">some</span><span begin="02:38.791" end="02:39.596">thin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是当我们谈论某件事时</span></p><p begin="02:40.210" end="02:44.634" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:40.210" end="02:40.276">We</span> <span begin="02:40.276" end="02:40.722">have</span> <span begin="02:40.722" end="02:42.026">good</span> <span begin="02:43.875" end="02:44.048">dis</span><span begin="02:44.048" end="02:44.239">cus</span><span begin="02:44.239" end="02:44.634">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可以很好地交流</span></p><p begin="02:47.205" end="02:53.175" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:47.205" end="02:47.360">I</span> <span begin="02:47.360" end="02:47.566">met</span> <span begin="02:47.566" end="02:47.796">his</span> <span begin="02:47.796" end="02:48.379">friends</span> <span begin="02:48.379" end="02:48.967">last</span> <span begin="02:48.967" end="02:49.487">week</span> <span begin="02:50.575" end="02:50.742">feels</span> <span begin="02:50.742" end="02:50.939">like</span> <span begin="02:50.939" end="02:51.204">they're</span> <span begin="02:51.204" end="02:51.766">up</span> <span begin="02:51.766" end="02:52.500">to</span> <span begin="02:52.500" end="02:52.719">some</span><span begin="02:52.719" end="02:53.175">thin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">上周我遇见了他的朋友 感觉像他们在策划什么事情</span></p><p begin="02:54.210" end="02:58.694" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin=