86" end="03:37.341">A</span><span begin="03:37.341" end="03:37.666">way</span> <span begin="03:37.666" end="03:37.897">turf</span> <span begin="03:37.897" end="03:38.172">no</span> <span begin="03:38.172" end="03:38.426">As</span><span begin="03:38.426" end="03:38.769">tro'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">超越现实 并非虚构</span></p><p begin="03:39.082" end="03:40.571" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="03:39.082" end="03:39.203">Mes</span><span begin="03:39.203" end="03:39.317">me</span><span begin="03:39.317" end="03:39.652">rized</span> <span begin="03:39.652" end="03:39.767">how</span> <span begin="03:39.767" end="03:39.955">the</span> <span begin="03:39.955" end="03:40.198">strobes</span> <span begin="03:40.198" end="03:40.571">glow</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为闪光灯发出的光而陶醉</span></p><p begin="03:40.848" end="03:42.249" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="03:40.848" end="03:40.901">Look</span> <span begin="03:40.901" end="03:41.021">at</span> <span begin="03:41.021" end="03:41.172">all</span> <span begin="03:41.172" end="03:41.366">the</span> <span begin="03:41.366" end="03:41.479">peo</span><span begin="03:41.479" end="03:41.669">ple</span> <span begin="03:41.669" end="03:41.930">feet</span> <span begin="03:41.930" end="03:42.249">dance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">看着所有的人都在跳舞</span></p><p begin="03:42.558" end="03:45.644" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="03:42.558" end="03:42.750">I</span> <span begin="03:42.750" end="03:42.887">know</span> <span begin="03:42.887" end="03:43.013">that</span> <span begin="03:43.013" end="03:43.195">your</span> <span begin="03:43.195" end="03:43.339">nig</span><span begin="03:43.339" end="03:43.541">ga</span> <span begin="03:43.541" end="03:44.027">came</span> <span begin="03:45.205" end="03:45.369">wit'</span> <span begin="03:45.369" end="03:45.644">ya</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道你的他也和你一同前往</span></p><p begin="03:46.642" end="03:49.243" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="03:46.642" end="03:46.793">But</span> <span begin="03:46.793" end="03:47.057">he</span> <span begin="03:47.057" end="03:47.482">ain't</span> <span begin="03:48.700" end="03:48.832">wit'</span> <span begin="03:48.832" end="03:49.243">ya</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是他没有和你在一起</span></p><p begin="03:49.394" end="03:51.508" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="03:49.394" end="03:49.565">The</span> <span begin="03:49.565" end="03:49.674">on</span><span begin="03:49.674" end="03:49.741">ly</span> <span begin="03:49.741" end="03:49.878">hu</span><span begin="03:49.878" end="03:50.005">man</span> <span begin="03:50.005" end="03:50.146">in</span> <span begin="03:50.146" end="03:50.349">this</span> <span begin="03:50.349" end="03:50.505">hu</span><span begin="03:50.505" end="03:50.644">mid</span> <span begin="03:50.644" end="03:50.826">in</span> <span begin="03:50.826" end="03:50.986">these</span> <span begin="03:50.986" end="03:51.212">Bal</span><span begin="03:51.212" end="03:51.508">mains</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们是这次法国时尚庄园中唯一身上潮湿的人</span></p><p begin="03:51.850" end="03:53.304" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="03:51.850" end="03:51.891">I</span> <span begin="03:51.891" end="03:51.966">mean</span> <span begin="03:51.966" end="03:52.157">my</span> <span begin="03:52.157" end="03:52.377">balls</span> <span begin="03:52.377" end="03:52.501">sti</span><span begin="03:52.501" end="03:52.708">ckin'</span> <span begin="03:52.708" end="03:52.830">in</span> <span begin="03:52.830" end="03:53.015">my</span> <span begin="03:53.015" end="03:53.304">jeans</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我意思是 我毁掉了我名贵的牛仔裤</span></p><p begin="03:53.517" end="03:55.022" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="03:53.517" end="03:53.633">We</span> <span begin="03:53.633" end="03:53.719">brea</span><span begin="03:53.719" end="03:53.929">thin'</span> <span begin="03:53.929" end="03:54.137">phere</span><span begin="03:54.137" end="03:54.454">mones,</span> <span begin="03:54.454" end="03:54.557">Am</span><span begin="03:54.557" end="03:54.721">ber</span> <span begin="03:54.721" end="03:55.022">Rose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们像艾波 罗丝那样去吸引别人</span></p><p begin="03:55.345" end="03:56.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L54"><span begin="03:55.345" end="03:55.440">Sip</span><span begin="03:55.440" end="03:55.618">pin'</span> <span begin="03:55.618" end="03:55.870">pink-</span><span begin="03:55.870" end="03:56.150">gold</span> <span begin="03:56.150" end="03:56.258">le</span><span begin="03:56.258" end="03:56.413">mo</span><span begin="03:56.413" end="03:56.730">nades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">小酌着带有柠檬的黄金啤酒</span></p><p begin="03:57.071" end="03:57.337" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L55"><span begin="03:57.071" end="03:57.144">Fee</span><span begin="03:57.144" end="03:57.337">lin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">内心这样感觉</span></p><p begin="03:58.355" end="04:02.943" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L56"><span begin="03:58.355" end="03:58.621">I</span> <span begin="03:58.621" end="03:58.843">may</span> <span begin="03:58.843" end="03:59.076">be</span> <span begin="03:59.076" end="03:59.322">youn</span><span begin="03:59.322" end="04:00.206">ger,</span> <span begin="04:00.490" end="04:00.643">but</span> <span begin="04:00.643" end="04:00.949">I'll</span> <span begin="04:00.949" end="04:01.272">look</span> <span begin="04:01.272" end="04:01.627">af</span><span begin="04:01.627" end="04:01.877">ter</span> <span begin="04:01.877" end="04:02.943">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我可能会更年轻 但我会照顾你</span></p><p begin="04:05.401" end="04:10.224" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L57"><span begin="04:05.401" end="04:05.650">We're</span> <span begin="04:05.650" end="04:05.865">not</span> <span begin="04:05.865" end="04:06.099">in</span> <span begin="04:06.099" end="04:07.118">love,</span> <span begin="04:07.402" end="04:07.616">but</span> <span begin="04:07.616" end="04:07.875">I'll</span> <span begin="04:07.875" end="04:08.227">make</span> <span begin="04:08.227" end="04:08.637">love</span> <span begin="04:08.637" end="04:08.851">to</span> <span begin="04:08.851" end="04:10.224">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们之间没有爱 但是我会向你示爱</span></p><p begin="04:12.143" end="04:17.096" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L58"><span begin="04:12.143" end="04:12.229">When</span> <span begin="04:12.229" end="04:12.664">you're</span> <span begin="04:12.664" end="04:13.051">not</span> <span begin="04:13.051" end="04:14.117">here,</span> <span begin="04:14.369" end="04:14.686">I'll</span> <span begin="04:14.686" end="04:15.126">save</span> <span begin="04:15.126" end="04:15.631">some</span> <span begin="04:15.631" end="04:15.905">for</span> <span begin="04:15.905" end="04:17.096">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你不在这儿时 我会为你保存些什么东西</span></p><p begin="04:19.485" end="04:24.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L59"><span begin="04:19.485" end="04:19.567">I'm</span> <span begin="04:19.567" end="04:20.062">not</span> <span begin="04:20.062" end="04:20.975">him,</span> <span begin="04:21.351" end="04:21.484">but</span> <span begin="04:21.484" end="04:21.807">I'll</span> <span begin="04:21.807" end="04:22.287">mean</span> <span begin="04:22.287" end="04:22.589">some</span><span begin="04:22.589" end="04:22.868">thin'</span> <span begin="04:22.868" end="04:23.299">to</span> <span begin="04:23.299" end="04:24.720">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不是他 但是我对你来说也有一定的意义</span></p><p begin="04:24.852" end="04:31.174" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L60"><span begin="04:24.852" end="04:25.125">I'll</span> <span begin="04:25.125" end="04:26.376">mean</span> <span begin="04:26.376" end="04:26.808">some</span><span begin="04:26.808" end="04:28.254">thing</span> <span begin="04:28.254" end="04:28.458">to</span> <span begin="04:28.458" end="04:31.174">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我对你来说也有一定的意义</span></p><p begin="04:31.861" end="04:38.313" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L61"><span begin="04:31.861" end="04:32.148">I'll</span> <span begin="04:32.148" end="04:33.438">mean</span> <span begin="04:33.438" end="04:33.965">some</span><span begin="04:33.965" end="04:35.327">thing</span> <span begin="04:35.327" end="04:36.497">to</span> <span begin="04:36.497" end="04:38.313">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我对你来说也有一定的意义</span></p><p begin="04:39.852" end="04:45.445" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L62"><span begin="04:39.852" end="04:40.134">You</span> <span begin="04:40.134" end="04:40.302">got</span> <span begin="04:40.302" end="04:40.556">a</span> <span begin="04:40.556" end="04:41.265">room</span><span begin="04:41.265" end="04:41.456">mate</span> <span begin="04:42.055" end="04:42.354">he'll</span> <span begin="04:42.354" end="04:42.801">hear</span> <span begin="04:42.801" end="04:43.238">what</span> <span begin="04:43.238" end="04:43.447">we</span> <span begin="04:43.447" end="04:45.445">do</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们有个室友 他会听到我们在做什么</span></p><p begin="04:46.836" end="04:52.802" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L63"><span begin="04:46.836" end="04:47.120">It's</span> <span begin="04:47.120" end="04:47.362">on</span><span begin="04:47.362" end="04:47.640">ly</span> <span begin="04:47.640" end="04:48.081">aw</span><span begin="04:48.081" end="04:48.594">kward</span> <span begin="04:48.904" end="04:49.057">if</span> <span begin="04:49.057" end="04:49.320">you're</span> <span begin="04:49.320" end="04:49.737">fu</span><span begin="04:49.737" end="04:50.010">cking</span> <span begin="04:50.010" end="04:50.435">him</span> <span begin="04:50.435" end="04:52.802">too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你也对他有兴趣的话 那只会觉得尴尬</span></p></div></body></tt>